---
import DashboardLayout from '../../../layouts/DashboardLayout.astro';
---
<DashboardLayout title="Configuraci&oacute;n avanzada &mdash; LBOT">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">

    <!-- Back -->
    <a href="/dashboard/tutorials"
       class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition mb-6 group">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:-translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
      </svg>
      Volver a tutoriales
    </a>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-3">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-600/20 text-purple-400">Pro</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 flex items-center gap-1">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
          43 min
        </span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Configuraci&oacute;n avanzada</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
        Descubre c&oacute;mo maximizar tu generaci&oacute;n de Teras con rutas avanzadas, loot personalizado
        y estrategias de farmeo multi-zona para el 2026.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Video embed -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 mb-6">
      <div class="relative w-full" style="padding-top: 56.25%;">
        <iframe
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
          src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/rfr_3kVBYkk?rel=0&modestbranding=1"
          title="HOW TO MAKE TERA IN DMO - GUIDE 2026"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy">
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Info cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Plataforma</p>
        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Digimon Masters Online</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Nivel</p>
        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Intermedio / Pro</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Zonas</p>
        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Western + Server</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tips -->
    <div class="bg-purple-600/5 border border-purple-600/20 rounded-2xl p-5">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
        Consejos clave de esta gu&iacute;a
      </h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>Configura m&uacute;ltiples rutas de respaldo para evitar saturaci&oacute;n</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>Usa el filtro de loot para no llenar el inventario con items sin valor</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>Ajusta el temporizador de pausa para evitar detecci&oacute;n</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>El plan Pro incluye rotaci&oacute;n autom&aacute;tica de servidores</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</DashboardLayout>
